objenome.solver.evolve.event

Interface Listener<T extends Event>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of events that this object will listen to
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdjustedFitnessFunction, BranchedBreeder, FitnessEvaluator, Full, GenerationalStrategy, Grow, HitsCount, HitsCountAndMinified, Initialiser, MaximumGenerations, OnePointCrossover, PointMutation, ProxyComponent, RampedHalfAndHalf, SubtreeCrossover, SubtreeMutation, SumOfError, TerminationFitness

    public interface Listener<T extends Event>
    The Listener interface implemented by any class whose instances are intended to receive notification about events generated during the execution of a run.
    See Also:
    Event, EventManager
